    "As ABC software's help center, consider the user model and write a user guide to inform the user on the installation of ABC software.\"",
    "It is important to note that the specified prompt is only an instance and other variations could be inputted based on the formula.",
    "As such, the defined formula is to act as a template at which writers can, then, develop prompts at their discretion.",
    "The intentions of the formula rely on the execution of a fitting response: content that meets the demands of the rhetorical situation and consequently solves the available problem.",
    "It is important to note that the defined formula has yet to be considered against tools such as ChatGPT, in which prompts are refined and modified through its dialogue feature-the formula is not to be received as single-use or disposable prompt engineering, but, instead, promotes an iterative process at the discretion of the writer."
